生词进行了讲解，并配以例句，每部分后还设计了练习。与初版相比，再版在以下两个方面有所提高和突破：一、在词根理论方面加强了科学性与系统性，增强了学术含量；二、在词根的选择和介绍、例句的内容以及练习的设计等方面更加注重其适用性和实用性。该书系国内少有的集理论性和实用性为一体的词根专著，适合高级程度的读者从事英语词汇学习与研究使用。","price":"18.90元"},"book_id":"3002766","id":973214010},{"status":"wish","updated":"2015-10-31 17:09:13","user_id":"2274326","tags":["等我有了ulimite"],"book":{"rating":{"max":10,"numRaters":1,"average":"0.0","min":0},"subtitle":"","author":["Talty, Stephan"],"pubdate":"2012-7","tags":[{"count":1,"name":"小说","title":"小说"},{"count":1,"name":"等我有了ulimite","title":"等我有了ulimite"}],"origin_title":"","image":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s24267018.jpg","binding":"","translator":[],"catalog":"","pages":"320","images":{"small":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/spic\/s24267018.jpg","large":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/lpic\/s24267018.jpg","medium":"https://img1.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s24267018.jpg"},"alt":"https:\/\/book.douban.com\/subject\/12055931\/","id":"12055931","publisher":"","isbn10":"0547614810","isbn13":"9780547614816","title":"Agent Garbo","url":"http:\/\/api.douban.com\/v2\/book\/12055931","alt_title":"","author_intro":"","summary":"","price":"$ 31.64"},"book_id":"12055931","id":972967116},{"status":"wish","updated":"2015-10-31 09:30:08","user_id":"2274326","book":{"rating":{"max":10,"numRaters":4029,"average":"9.1","min":0},"subtitle":"","author":["[美] 安·兰德"],"pubdate":"2005-11","tags":[{"count":2986,"name":"安·兰德","title":"安·兰德"},{"count":1958,"name":"小说","title":"小说"},{"count":1283,"name":"个人主义","title":"个人主义"},{"count":1008,"name":"美国","title":"美国"},{"count":958,"name":"哲学","title":"哲学"},{"count":763,"name":"源泉","title":"源泉"},{"count":749,"name":"外国文学","title":"外国文学"},{"count":686,"name":"理想，勇气，爱","title":"理想，勇气，爱"}],"origin_title":"Fountainhead","image":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s1451416.jpg","binding":"平装","translator":["高晓晴","赵雅蔷","杨玉"],"catalog":"第一部分 彼得•吉丁\n第二部分 埃斯沃斯•托黑\n第三部分 盖尔•华纳德\n第四部分 霍德华•洛克","pages":"706","images":{"small":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/spic\/s1451416.jpg","large":"https://img